  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates the anticancer potential of bioactive glass nanoparticles against triple-negative breast cancer through multiple mechanisms including ROS generation, mitochondrial dysfunction, and p53-dependent apoptosis.",
    "The IC50 value of 184.3 \u00b5g/ml was determined for BGNps cytotoxicity in MDA-MB-231 cells after 72 hours of treatment.",
    "The study provides mechanistic insights into BGNps-induced cell death involving upregulation of p53 and downregulation of Bcl-2 and ND3 genes."
  ]
